arts.ttl: Young Boys end campaign without a point after Red Star loss
arts.sum: Red Star Belgrade secure a 1-0 win over Young Boys to leave the Swiss champions on no points to end their Champions League campaign.

arts.ttl: Daizen Maeda blow as Celtic star hit with TWO game Champions League ban over Young Boys red card
arts.sum: The Japanese wide man saw red late on in the 1-0 victory against Young Boys at Parkhead last week that clinched a Champions League play-off spot for the Hoops
